14300:Letting it burst forth...[%p]
14400:The sound disappeared. The light vanished.[%p]
14500:Sena and I were standing there,[%p]
14600:silently, in the middle of the dead, ruined city.[%p]
14700:Sena was clinging to me, and I was leaning up against her. We were holding the bloody baby between us.[%p]
14800:I couldn't move another step. I couldn't move an inch. I didn't have the strength left.[%p]
14900:[name]セナ[line]Enough.[%p]
15000:[name]セナ[line]It's sad... but that's enough.[%p]
15100:[name]セナ[line]It's selfish to want to bring back the dead.[%p]
15200:[name]セナ[line]Let's give back the cheat code.[%p]
15300:I agreed. And we were alive. We had to live our lives for the sake of those who had died.[%p]
15400:[name]セナ[line]I'm sorry.[%p]
15500:Sena softly held the bloody baby.[%p]
15600:[name]セナ[line]I'm sorry.[%p]
15700:[name]セナ[line]I'm sorry I let you die.[%p]
15800:Sena sure was crying a lot today.[%p]
15900:But she was a lot prettier now than she was[%p]
16000:when she was mad at everybody all the time.[%p]
16100:And her tears were beautiful, too.[%p]
16200:I thought about that as I looked up at the night sky.[%p]
